<h1>DAISY Book Image Description Tool</h1>
<p>
To insert image descriptions into a DAISY book from the Bookshare library, follow these steps:
</p>
<ol>
<li>Click the Browse button (below) and choose a DAISY book (zip) file from your local drive to upload.</li>
<li>If the book is password protected, enter your password in the field.</li>
<li>Click the Upload button.</li>
</ol>
<p>
Any existing image descriptions will be added to the book, 
and the book will be returned to you as a new DAISY book (zip) file.
</p>

<%= form_tag("/daisy_book/submit_to_get_descriptions", {:multipart => true}) do %>
<p><label for="upload_file">Select Daisy book file</label> : 
<%= file_field_tag 'book' %> </p>
<p><label for="upload_file">Enter password (if needed)</label> :
<%= password_field_tag 'password' %> </p>
<%= submit_tag "Process" %>
<% end %>

